com.paypal.selion.platform.mobile.android

Class UiObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.platform.mobile.android.UiObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    UserinterfaceObject
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UiButton, UiTextView

    public class UiObject
extends Object
implements UserinterfaceObject
    UiObject implements UserinterfaceObject and forms the base class of all Android UI automation elements.
